## 5. Timely

### Overview
- **Market Position:** AI-powered automatic tracker (agencies, consultancies)
- **Users:** 100K+
- **Pricing:** $9-20/user/mo

### Strengths
- ✅ **Memory Tracker:** Automatic capture of all activity (apps, files, websites)
- ✅ **AI timesheets:** AI suggests time entries based on tracked activity
- ✅ **Privacy controls:** Memories are private until user shares
- ✅ **3 AI styles:** Exact (minute-by-minute), Efficient (balanced), Concise (simplified)
- ✅ **Team features:** Project budgets, forecasting

### Weaknesses
- ❌ **Cloud-first:** All data on Timely servers
- ❌ **Expensive:** No free tier
- ❌ **AI over-reliance:** Some users want manual control
- ❌ **Memory app required:** Desktop app installation

### AI Features (Inspiration)
- **Timesheet Assistant:** Reviews tracked activities → auto-organizes into projects
- **Smart categorization:** Learns user's work patterns over time
- **AI styles:** Different levels of granularity (good UX idea)

**Neuman Brain Adaptation:** Offer manual + AI hybrid (user chooses, not forced).

