## 7. Developer-Focused Tools

### WakaTime
- **What it is:** IDE plugin that tracks coding time
- **Pricing:** Free (public profiles) → $10/mo (private)
- **Strengths:** Automatic, editor-native, language/project breakdown
- **Weaknesses:** Coding only (no meetings, emails, etc.)

