- **Weaknesses:** Not focused on time tracking

### Super Productivity
- **What it is:** Open-source productivity app
- **Pricing:** Free
- **Strengths:** Offline-first, privacy-focused, integrations
- **Weaknesses:** Less polished than commercial tools

**Developer Needs:**
- CLI interface (or at least keyboard-first)
- Git integration (auto-switch project based on branch)
- IDE plugins (WakaTime-style)
- Fast, no-nonsense UX (Linear-style)

**Neuman Brain Opportunity:** We can be the **best developer time tracker** with keyboard shortcuts, CLI (future), Git integration, and privacy.

